{
  "stem": "6989.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- I don't know what happened to the things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they just locked up and walked out with the packages, whatever they could take in their hands, and thinking that they would be back or, you know, that it would last maybe a couple of weeks or months and they'll be back.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would not know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I only remember what was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember being excited, because my grandma was there, whom I loved very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And being closer with everyone else, there were more children to play with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I also remember that my aunt was married to her husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] his name was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember that he was-- he had been in, I think, in Lwow to visit family of his.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when he came back that day-- because I remember my parents saying that on the street, like many times, if you were on the street, you would get killed immediately.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, like, if we knew, if somebody said the Germans are coming, everybody went into their houses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was killed in that first [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans entered the ghetto--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my first thing that I knew, the person, the first person that I ever knew of that got-- that was killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, the fear was always there, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was constricted to work, some kind of work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what kind of work, but you know, leave early in the morning and  come--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Taken to work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, they used to-- not just him, you know, a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember her being taken anywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
